  <original-body>When using config.gem, if you specify a version requirement like '&gt;=1.0.0' Rails will only load unpacked gems with this exact version. Newer gems are not loaded; so if you have the version 1.1 of this gem in your vendor Rails won't load it.

Attached is a patch to make gem_dependency load any gem on vendor that matches the gem requirement.</original-body>
